result.name: Highly evolvable malaria vectors: The genomes of 16 Anopheles mosquitoes. Anopheles melas samples.
result.description: Anopheles melas subset of project sequencing 16 anopheline vector genomes to complement and facilitate comparative analysis with the three other sequenced anophelines, Anopheles gambiae PEST, M and S forms. This subsection of the project contains data for Anopheles arabiensis.
